name: DC865
body:
## WHAT
DC865 is Knoxville's local DefCon Chapter - A meeting of hackers, wannabe hackers, and like-minded folk.

## WHEN/WHERE

8-10pm
Every third Wednesday of the month

1010 Commerce Park Drive
Oak Ridge, TN

## RESOURCES
https://basecamp.com/2050885/projects/2195053-knoxville-def-con
